​Improvement Strategy for Identified Weaknesses
​To transform these operational weaknesses into development strengths, I am adopting a comprehensive "defensive programming" framework for all future software projects. Rather than focusing solely on successful data transactions, I will dedicate the first phase of my development sprints to architecting holistic error-catching and logging structures.
